{"tid":1920293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何猷君帶領翻牆 指叫中國人道歉「吃屎吧」","createTime":"2020-03-11T11:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T11:18:53.000Z","uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a14c9f0f093847cd21389149de3ad71143ce6650","tid":1920293,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1660125?from=fb_et_star\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1660125%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_star&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=9423a826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1660125?from=fb_et_star</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何猷君4日氣憤發文：「我找到這個SB（大陸俗語：傻屄，意旨傻子）的Instagram了，有空的網友麻煩翻牆一起幫忙罵，謝謝。要我們中國人道歉？吃屎吧。」一開始還有網友並不知道前情詢問，他一一回覆：「這個傻B在電視直播中要求我們中國人道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n微博貼文附圖中，可以看見何猷君用英文發文並標記傑西沃特斯，痛批：「如果你想要一句道歉的話這裡有，我想代表我國說一句『我們全體人民對你爸媽感到十分抱歉』，我們很抱歉你爸媽經歷9個多月孕期、花費數十年的時間、金錢和努力卻生成了全宇宙最糟糕的爛人，是的，我們很抱歉，但並不是為了新冠肺炎（更何況我們防疫做得很好），而是因為你的父母悲哀地必須得忍受你一輩子，FXXX YOU.」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一齊去舉行佢ig la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎就武漢肺炎<br />\n中國就係要道歉<br />\n唔道歉仲要叫人去翻牆留言<br />\n識唔識寫個醜字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何猷君instagram: @momomarioho<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/momomarioho?igshid=883t1c70zxx3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmomomarioho%3Figshid%3D883t1c70zxx3&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ee35a523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/momomarioho?igshid=883t1c70zxx3</a>"},{"pid":"0affa4dc59a6467ba9a2520e5b8843c9636b5e2d","tid":1920293,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"何氏後人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠晒丢架"},{"pid":"f6f32029d231601162ccdd2f06ffbe6a1dabed2e","tid":1920293,"uid":313222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"公然叫人翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8bfff9f213863592809d9f21b4e8645ef7024b","tid":1920293,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"佢個腦俾大陸西水染紅左"},{"pid":"7634384c0023aa17b76524e2a67872a017d365ea","tid":1920293,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"老婆係支那人 晚晚奶共"}]}